profile:
Home Painters Toronto

If you're looking for a professional painting and home renovation company with years of experience to prove it, then look no further, Home Painters Toronto is the contractor for you. We specialize in interior, exterior, residential, and commercial painting and our services don't stop there! We can also help you with drywall repair and installation, plaster, stucco ceiling repair and removal, carpentry, Kitchen Cabinet repainting, hardwood flooring and much more! Call one of our customer service experts now and be well on your way to a quote and a beautifully transformed property.

Serving Toronto and the regional Municipalities of York, Halton, Peel, Durham, and more!   

Remember when you go with Home Painters we value your business and referrals and are committed to getting it done right the first time. GUARANTEED!

Why use Home Painters to paint your house/office?
•Two Year Guarantee On All Work Done
•Full Workers Compensation
•5 Million Liability Insurance
•Fully Bonded Workers (Criminal Background Checks on ALL Workers)
•30 Years Experience in the Painting Industry
•Thousands of Satisfied Clients
•Top Quality Paints Used Including Benjamin Moore, Dulux, Behr, Sherwin Williams, Para etc
•Drop sheets to Protect Your Floors and Belongings
•100% Satisfaction Guaranteed!!

 Interior Painting Services Include:
•Painting (i.e. walls, trim, doors, floors, ceilings, etc.)
•Staining (i.e. banisters, hardwood floors, cabinets, etc.)
•Faux finishing  
•Stucco Painting and Repair
•Wallpapering and Removal 
•Drywall Repair and Replacement
•Plaster

 Exterior Painting Services Include:
•Painting Exterior Surfaces (ie. windows, brick, doors, eaves, soffits, aluminum siding, etc.)
•Deck/Fence Staining and Refinishing
•Power Washing 
•Caulking 
•Rotten Wood Replacement/Repair

profile:
The Perfect Painter is resuming operations and scheduling free estimates for all your Residential and Painting Needs

We are pleased to announce that all Residential renovations are deemed essential, both new and ongoing renovations including painting can continue as per the Provincial Government.

We have also expanded our service areas to include Burlington, Oakville, Milton, Mississauga, Brampton, Toronto, Vaughan, Markham, Newmarket, Aurora, Stouffville, Pickering and Oshawa.

We are GTA'S Top Professional Painting company, with highly skilled trades and a great reputation for customer service. We specialize in Interior & Exterior Painting, Custom Cabinet Refinishing, Staining  and  Staircase Refinishing . We are experts in residential homes and commercial offices. We do complete Home Renovations and we are a licenced General Contractor all in one. We have 3 divisions,  Perfect Painter, Perfect Handyman & Affinity Home Renovations, we are your "One Stop Shop" for all your renovation needs.. We are the only company in Toronto and GTA market that provides Full Services on almost all aspects of Home Renovations within one Team. We have award winning customer service and pride ourselves on making everything right. Having one team that is responsible for all your home or commercial renovation has great value both from quality, accountability and scheduling. From design and build and to as little as our 4 hour handyman repair service, we can accommodate all your needs.

We are the fastest growing Painting and Home Renovation Company in Toronto and the GTA. Our Handymen and Home Renovation Divisions are all Full Service. We have 24 exceptional Professional Painters hand-picked  and 22  finished carpenters/handyman/skilled trades, they are also Hand-picked. We only hire the best people possible and stand behind all work we do. From small Painting jobs to Handyman Jobs to painting your home and office, we can accommodate all your needs.  Our renovation teams  can complete full condo to home renovations even from the Design and build stages with our skilled staff. Our  highly skilled Field Managers bring an average of 20 years of Construction experience and renovation experience to our company.  We have a real warranty, we will come back and fix something without the fear of people not answering your call or making excuses, we stand behind the work we do.
 
Perfect Painters can provide you with certified color consultants and interior designers. We recommend the best quality paints from Sherwin William, Benjamin Moore or Dulux. We also understand that painting prices need to be competitive and we will always compete to earn your business and trust.  
 
 
We offer our customers the opportunity to purchase paint at our wholesale prices. Perfect Painter is a  custom painting company,  but we don’t charge a custom price. We want to grow our business long term so that we will become the house painters for you and your family. Do not forget to look at our Painting Specials and remember we provide our painting services in the following communities: Aurora, , Brampton, Burlington, Bolton, Caledon, King City, Mississauga, Milton, Maple, Georgetown, Oakville, Richmond Hill, Markham, Vaughan, Etobicoke, Toronto and all of the GTA. We are your Painting company in the GTA.
 


Perfect Painter’s take pride in performing our work to exceed your standard. We will leave your commercial or residential space clean and tidy so it is usable for your clients and family after we have completed our assignment. Please allow us to visit your site/home/office and provide you with an accurate free estimate. We can advise you on the painting work that will be required at that time and make suggestions on color, decor and finishes. Our painting quotes contain a detailed breakdown of costs and the specific work to be done, the painting materials, and an estimate of the amount of time the painting will take. We are also able to offer other services such as drywall and taping at a fraction of the cost of other companies. Prompt, reliable and efficient services – we assure our clients the best quality painting job for your home or your business. 
 
 
 
At Perfect Painter, we have full liability insurance and our staff is covered by WSIB. Most companies fail to meet this criteria almost 83% of the time.
 
Remember you home is typically your largest asset so don’t take chances on losing it by fly by night companies. We understand our business is competitive and we will earn your business each and every time.

profile:
Absolute Home Services is a one stop shop for all of your home services. We currently specialize in:
 
1. Interior and Exterior Painting
2. Handyman Services
3. Lawn and Garden Maintenance
4. Landscaping
5. Interlock

 
Please contact us through email, website or phone call. The PING messaging service does not work well for communication purposes.
 
Customer satisfaction and retention is our primary focus. Therefore, we will do whatever it takes to ensure you are happy with our quality and service. Our goal is to have a customer for life! We want you to use us for all of our services, so we ensure you are happy after each service you use.
 
We service:
 
Mississauga, Oakville, Burlington, Hamilton, Milton, Toronto, Vaughan, Aurora, Newmarket, Barrie and Muskoka
 
We work on both commercial and residential projects.
 
Whether we are landscaping or painting, we have experienced people in each of their trades. Our painters take pride in what they do and are passionate providing high quality paint jobs. We have experts in interlock, lawn care and garden services who will give you the advice you need and a professional job.
 
Our service is what sets us a part from the rest. We have great people to provide great quality work, but we also have a goal to retain our customers for multiple services. In order to achieve this goal, we need to provide clear expectations, detailed quotes, communicate and deliver what we promise.
service_area: We service the GTA including Hamilton, Burlington, Oakville, MIlton, Mississsauga, Etobicoke, Barrie, Newmarket, Aurora, Vaughan and Muskoka areas. We will also service Toronto for some of services. We don't service Toronto for lawn cutting and gardening unfortunately.

profile:
We are Design+Build company having all the professionals from A-Z  in our team. 
Before you do anything, give us a call as we are Design + Build company with Tarion new home builder, Structure engineer with 'PNG' license and working with some of the best Interior design and Architectural firms in Toronto. You will be saving so much money by choosing us instead of waisting your money by hiring a individual companies for each task. 

Based in Toronto, 'Fresh Home Innovations' has been a leader in residential renovations and custom home construction since 2000. From concept to completion, we take a client’s vision and make it a reality through a comprehensive process to ensure the finished product exceeds expectations. Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your project. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, freshhomeinnovations.com  is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.

Our wealth of experience, skilled expertise and attention to detail enables us to offer you innovative solutions, competitive pricing and the ability to meet milestones. We appreciate how much your project means to you. That’s why we approach each project with professionalism, integrity and adaptability while maintaining open communication with you every step of the way. 
We pride ourselves in Home additions, renovations, custom home building, commercial renovations, condominium renovations and design and build projects.  Let us partner with you to create the home of your dreams.

We understand the family home is the most important investment most people will make in their lifetime, and you as our client have entrusted your investment to us. So whether it be a new architecturally designed or inspired home, or a renovation and extension of your existing home, you can be guaranteed that Fresh Home Innovations  is most definitely the qualified team for your project.
Our friendly, jovial and courteous staff receive ongoing training to ensure we can deliver this promise to you on a daily basis. 

 We have had the opportunity to transform your dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. We have enjoyed being a part of homeowners’ lives and strive to continue to provide our customers with the best technology on the market. We have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at freshhomeinnovations.com to view images of some of our projects.  
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship. 

Our projects range from building new custom homes, home additions and extensions, condominium renovations, architectural design and permit, structural engineering, commercial renovations, rear addition, second floor addition, basement underpinning, historical restoration, custom projects, general contracting, custom kitchen and bathrooms, residential renovations and finally we design and build everything. We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 

With a minimum 2 year Warranty, we at freshhomeinnovations.com  know how to design and build lasting results and lasting relationships with each of our highly respected clients. 
Our focus is on Custom projects such as custom Kitchen renovations, Basement Finishing and underpinning, Bathroom Renovation and Bathroom Remodeling, Home Additions, Second Story Additions, Rear Additions, Home Extensions and Rear Extensions, commercial renovations, office renovation, architectural drawings, permit and etc. We work with some of the top architects, interior designers, engineers and sub-trades in Toronto. We provide custom marble and tile install services as our marble and tile setters are highly skilled and detail oriented. We are the all inclusive General Contractor who will take care of all your design and general contracting needs.

Fresh Home Innovations is an innovative, full service design/build/ construction firm based in Toronto, specializing in residential clients across the GTA. With decades of construction management experience on a wide variety of residential projects, we offer a strong design aesthetic, invaluable insight, vast resources and craftsman that exceed client expectations.
Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling, cost control, and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

There’s many different reasons to work with us: to make room for a growing family, to improve layout or increase the resale value of your property! Our team of professionals offer customers design and build counselling along with skilled trades and top discounts, on top brands. 

There is no substitute for experience. Join the list of satisfied clients! In the end the quality of your project depends on who you hire. When you hire us, you do so because of our company’s reputation, our track record with past clients and our commitment to new ones. The registered DesignBar trademark provides DIY home owners a single source for their residential design and construction needs when buying or selling homes in the GTA.

Future Perfect Construction is a local skilled construction firm founded in 2000 by a select group of individuals with a high level of expertise in the trade. The firm specializes in Commercial and Residential Renovations, Home Inspections, New Home Builds and Construction Project Management. Future Perfect's primary goal of meeting customer's needs through quality workmanship has resulted in the pride, loyalty and trust that co-insides with our standard of excellence. The firm is always working with it's clients to exceed standards, adhere to budgets and manage strict timelines. 
We believe that the value of the dollar has come a long way so we provide our services and do business with the utmost professionalism. We aim to service customers from the initial phase of planning and cost estimates to the final stages of our warranty process. 
Contact us for a free "No Pressure" estimate and let us help you take the first step to completing your project. Advice is always free.

profile:
ABOUT US

Odd Job Handyman Services began in 2008 with one man and his truck. It's since grown to be one of the largest and most reliable contractors in Toronto, serving thousands of homeowners and businesses throughout the city. On Feb. 16, 2017, it was one of five handyman services in Ontario to be officially named "Best of 2017" by Homestars, the largest network of home professionals in Canada. 

Odd Job offers a wide range of services including drywall, painting, tiling, flooring, millwork, hanging, junk removal, furniture assembly, basic plumbing & electrical and all general repairs. The work performed by Odd Job is covered by a two-year warranty. 

The staff at Odd Job is fully licensed, bonded and insured, and every member has been background-and-identity-checked. They're hand-selected from the "best of the best" in local professional circles (each with at least three positive references) and subjected to a series of in-shop tests before they're admitted into the team. 

HISTORY

It all started with Justin George, an exceptionally-handy property manager who had great difficulty convincing professional contractors to visit his building for "small jobs." Justin, a red seal tradesman, was so tired of contractors telling him "it wasn't worth their time" that he was forced to take care of most of the repairs and maintenance himself.

He realized he was far from the only person who was in this predicament. There were many people without the time, the tools or the talent to recaulk their shower stall, hang their favourite paintings or repair a few pot lights. 

Not everyone trusts the mystery men on Craigslist and Kijiji, and so Justin wanted to provide them a professional option. "It might be a small job, but it's a big deal," Justin said, "People need a company that treats it that way."

Mr. George graduated from George Brown College with a degree in mechanical engineering and from the University of Western Ontario in 2011 with a degree in technological education, manufacturing and construction. He is an Accredited Manufacturing and Construction Educator and a member in good standing of the Association of Certified Handyman Professionals (ACHP). He loves cats, guitar and building things (anything). His most important values are honesty, quality and consistency and his motto is: "There's always a way to get the job done right." 

PRICING

We offer a la carte, task-based pricing for all of our standard services. Our extensive experience has given us a tried-and-true system for evaluating the duration and cost for virtually every standard project." 

BUSINESS & PROPERTY MANAGEMENT SERVICES

Odd Job also serves many small businesses, including retail stores, office facilities and income properties. Our project manager was a longtime property manager and every member of the team has extensive experience in facilities management. Among the many businesses that trust Odd Job are Shoppers Drug Mart, Holt Renfrew, Burberry, Fresh Restaurants and LensCrafters.

Let us take care of you while you take care of business!

profile:
Why Choose House & Condo Painters?
 
Here at House & Condo Painters we are proud to say that we are one of the best Residential and Commercial Painting Contractors in Toronto. With over 25 years experience, we promise our clients to provide the highest quality painting and contracting services at highly competitive rates. We guarantee by the end of the project you will have an environment as unique as you!
 
To make this possible we offer to all clients:    
Outstanding Customer Service: Our staff are available to answer any and all of your questions. Your inquiries will be responded quickly, and regardless of your schedule!
 
Free In-Home Colour Consultations: House & Condo Painters specially provide free colour consultation before starting the job. We will give you our professional opinion on the colour and finish combinations that will make your home as you dream!
 
Following “Eco-Friendly” Processes: We only use high-quality trusted products to deliver the best results for your home. Often working with brands such as Benjamin Moore, Sherwin Williams, Behr, Dulux, Para, and more! We prioritize the use of paints with low VOCs to address any potential environmental concerns. Any leftover paint is saved for touch-ups, recycled  or donated to charity to minimize any unneeded waste.
 
Experienced Professionals: At House & Condo Painters we only hire professional, skilled painters for all of our projects. This helps us to ensure that the work we provide is of the highest quality and completed within the shortest amount of time.

profile:
At Silicone Seals, our goal is to make sure you get quality service for what you need.
 We specialize in a variety of services to take care of the big and small things your home needs.
 Whether you need sealant in your bathroom, or caulking around windows and doors, we got you covered.

We believe that our exceptional customer service, and quality work makes many happy customers. Contact us today to get a FREE QUOTE for your home.
services:
Our Primary Services:

- replacing caulking that is moldy and falling apart in your bathroom or kitchen

- caulking and sealing around masonry, concrete, decking/porch, and foundations

- draft sealing (foaming), using the highest quality low, medium, and high expansion foam and insulations, from todays leading manufactures. Let us get rid of those cold air drafts inside your home, and get you winter ready

- repairing or replacing caulking around windows and doors, using the highest grade of, silicone, polyurethane, acrylic or elastomeric sealants 

- caulking new windows and doors (new construction or installation) 

- Indoor and outdoor 

We also specialize in:
- repairing Interior water/moisture damage due to failed caulking or leaks, including drywall, ceiling, and floor repair.

- window and door trim repair.

- weather striping and threshold installation 

- stud and joist repair/replacing. Painting/repainting damaged or new surfaces. 

- epoxy and acrylic sealers over concrete, masonry, hardscaping and many other surfaces 

- restoring, staining and sealing wooden decks, fences, gazebos and docks 

- power washing and refreshing old masonry and concrete 

- we also offer grading and hardscaping as part of improving your homes water diversion, and prevent icing. Including, limestone screening, weed barrier, gravel, HPB, decorative river/quarry rock, interlocking, retaining wall, (both masonry, and lumber) and flag stone repairs and installation.

profile:
•	Exceptional family-owned business 
•	With 27 years of experience
•	100% positive feedback by customers 
Two brothers founded the company after years of working with their father for one of the largest window companies for 27 years.
They knew they wanted to fix people's homes with the same quality work their father instilled in them.
Fast forward to 1988. The brothers ran into an old friend who was doing remodeling, a partnership was formed. This was the beginning of the path that eventually led to " Brothers Window Works ".
The top two management team members have over 55 years experience in the home renewal industry. Customer-centric service is what the employees at " Brothers Window Works " provide - Experience high quality products backed by quality service.
" Brothers Window Works " is insured and bonded with an A+ rating from the Better Business Bureau. The company takes full responsibility every step of the way - from the initial consultation to providing maintenance services years after the project was completed. 
" Brothers Window Works " high standards of quality, ethics and integrity are unmatched in the home renewal industry.

profile:
As a general contracting business, Celio Group Incorporated has  been dedicated to building a company people can rely on.  Our mission is the philosophy of Progress and Success. With the care and quality that comes with an old world workmanship and ethic, and the ability that comes with a new world approach for design and construction, progress and success, has become a reality in every project for both Celio Group Incorporated and its clients. The company prides itself on reputation, and is committed to staying true to the same philosophy that has allowed for such success  regardless of scale or size of a project.  Celio Group Inc. has partnered with  Richwood Quality Kitchen and Bath Inc., who also prides itself with the same philosophy.  Both companies are equipped to take on full scale projects with quality service.

Specializing in:
    Kitchen Renovations
    Bathroom Renovations
    Handicap Accessibility
    Older Homes
    Commercial Units
A home renovation can be a stressful event and sometimes even daunting task for the first timer. Allow the staff at Celio Group Inc. to guide you through your project with expertise and quality workmanship. Let us handle the stress and give you the opportunity to enjoy the final product as we transform your current space to the room of your dreams.

Are you ready to renovate? Everyone has an idea of what is involved when renovating a space but are you prepared for the emotional journey you are about to embark on? Larger renovations tend to increase these feelings which will only bring on undue stress. Let Celio Group Inc. help alleviate these feelings as our team of experts complete your renovation.

Now in its thirteenth year of operation, Celio Group Inc. is growing in size and stature. The company prides itself on reputation, and is committed to staying true to the same philosophy that has allowed for such success on every project regardless of scale or size. Our policy is to create realistic estimates and budgets for the customer that accurately reflect what it takes to get the work completed properly by properlylicensed trades people.
